WEBVTT

00:00:26.624 --> 00:00:31.549
Ila kwa kuanza, nitawaambia
hadithi kutoka kwa Bwana Richard Messina,

00:00:31.573 --> 00:00:34.702
ambaye ni rafiki yangu na mkuu wa
shule ya msingi.

00:00:35.266 --> 00:00:36.827
Alipokea simu siku moja.

00:00:39.279 --> 00:00:40.430
Aliyepiga akasema,

00:00:40.454 --> 00:00:44.336
"Bwana Messina, mtoto wangu Johnny
hatakuja shuleni leo

00:00:44.360 --> 00:00:45.823
kwasababu anaumwa."

00:00:46.498 --> 00:00:48.234
Bwana Messina akauliza,

00:00:48.258 --> 00:00:50.272
"Naongea na nani, tafadhali?"

00:00:50.788 --> 00:00:52.278
Na aliyepiga akasema,

00:00:52.302 --> 00:00:53.967
"Mimi ni baba yangu."

00:00:53.991 --> 00:00:56.778
(Kicheko)

00:00:58.227 --> 00:00:59.909
Sasa hadithi hii --

00:00:59.933 --> 00:01:01.465
(Vicheko)